      <item>
        <title>Per_page limit on post (wp:contentmedia)</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[luisherranz]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Unfortunately that’s a limitation of the WP REST API. If you have more than 100 items you have to do multiple requests.</p>
<p>Are you using our old plugin or are you doing the requests yourself?</p>
          <p><a href="https://community.frontity.org/t/per-page-limit-on-post-wp-contentmedia/947/2">Read full topic</a></p>
